    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Team</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">多様な背景を持つメンバーが一致団結</p>
    </div>

    <div class="staff-grid">
      <div class="staff-card fade-in">
        <div class="staff-avatar">
